Use Python 3.11+

Open PowerShell in the project folder.

Create  virtual environment
python -m venv .venv

Activate your virtual environment

Powershell prompts:
python -m pip install pandas numpy yfinance

python -m pip install fredapi

$env:FRED_API_KEY = "YOUR API KEY"

$env:PYTHONPATH = "src"
python examples\run_csrm_example.py


The main file to run is run_csrm_example.py
